reviews.review_text:
Skull & Roses songs... This is the Skullfuck Playin' and Hog For You. Looks like Merl overdubbed some organ for the final release! Great lazy '71 show! Enjoy.

Dabeard1 - Yes I realize that Pig is playing the organ on this recording, but the Playin' in the Band and Hog For You on the Skull and Roses album are overdubbed by Merl Saunders. The live versions you hear on this recording were taken into the studio and touched up for the official release. For some reason, the Dead stopped using Pig's organ in the studio for the most part until 1972.

Jimbo - I'm A Hog For You is now included on the remastered release.
